s://web.facebook.com/GvnJoshuaIrungu','string','2026-03-24 09:53:47','2026-05-13 13:47:08'),(20,'social_youtube','https://web.facebook.com/GvnJoshuaIrungu','string','2026-03-24 09:53:47','2026-05-13 13:47:08'),(21,'items_per_page','12','string','2026-03-24 09:53:47','2026-05-13 13:47:08'),(22,'enable_comments','0','boolean','2026-03-24 09:53:47','2026-03-24 09:53:47'),(23,'show_home_hero','1','boolean','2026-03-24 09:53:47','2026-03-24 09:53:47'),(24,'show_home_posts','1','boolean','2026-03-24 09:53:47','2026-03-24 09:53:47'),(25,'show_home_announcements','1','boolean','2026-03-24 09:53:47','2026-03-24 09:53:47'),(26,'show_home_testimonials','1','boolean','2026-03-24 09:53:47','2026-03-24 09:53:47'),(27,'show_home_explore','0','boolean','2026-03-24 09:53:47','2026-05-13 13:39:00'),(28,'home_hero_image','hero/UnWKYMKGkoZNQEC4fnXcnDaZ5QUD5aGfIJums9fd.jpg','string','2026-03-24 09:53:49','2026-05-13 13:39:00'),(29,'home_governor_name','H.E Joshua Irungu, EGH','string','2026-05-13 13:39:00','2026-05-13 13:47:08'),(30,'home_governor_title','Governor','string','2026-05-13 13:39:00','2026-05-13 13:47:08'),(31,'home_governor_badge_title','Laikipia County','string','2026-05-13 13:39:00','2026-05-13 13:47:08'),(32,'home_governor_section_label',NULL,'string','2026-05-13 13:39:00','2026-05-13 13:39:00'),(33,'home_governor_heading_line_one',NULL,'string','2026-05-13 13:39:00','2026-05-13 13:39:00'),(34,'home_governor_heading_line_two',NULL,'string','2026-05-13 13:39:00','2026-05-13 13:39:00'),(35,'home_governor_subtitle',NULL,'string','2026-05-13 13:39:00','2026-05-13 13:39:00'),(36,'home_governor_intro','The ECDE Management Information System (ECDE-MIS) is a digital platform designed to enhance the management and delivery of early childhood education services across Laikipia County. It enables efficient data collection, real-time monitoring, and informed decision-making to improve the quality and accessibility of ECDE programmes.','text','2026-05-13 13:39:00','2026-05-13 13:47:08'),(37,'home_governor_quote','The County Government of Laikipia remains committed to strengthening Early Childhood Development Education (ECDE) as a critical foundation for our children’s future. The introduction of the ECDE Management Information System (ECDE-MIS) marks a significant step towards improving service delivery across all ECDE centres in the County.\r\n\r\nThis system will enable efficient data management, real-time monitoring, and informed decision-making on key areas such as learner enrolment, teacher deployment, and resource allocation. It will enhance transparency, accountability, and overall efficiency within the ECDE sector.\r\n\r\nI urge all stakeholders to embrace and fully utilize the ECDE-MIS to ensure quality and equitable early childhood education for every child in Laikipia County.\r\n\r\nTogether, we are building a stronger future.','text','2026-05-13 13:39:00','2026-05-13 13:47:08'),(38,'home_governor_cta_text',NULL,'string','2026-05-13 13:39:00','2026-05-13 13:39:00'),(39,'home_governor_message_url','Read Full Message','string','2026-05-13 13:39:00','2026-05-13 13:47:08'),(40,'home_governor_image','governor/hHlqeIDNCrVBYNcau7ZZs9LP8gVY76bo0cJVifeK.jpg','string','2026-05-13 13:39:00','2026-05-13 13:39:00');
