kipia.\",\"status\":\"published\",\"order\":3,\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-13T13:54:45.000000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2026-05-13T13:54:45.000000Z\",\"id\":3}','','2026-05-13 13:54:45','2026-05-13 13:54:45','faqs'),(2138,'1','105.160.6.33','Unknown','0','index',NULL,'User accessed the FAQs index page','admin/cms/faqs','{}','{}','','2026-05-13 13:54:46','2026-05-13 13:54:46','faqs'),(2139,'1','105.160.6.33','Unknown','0','create',NULL,'User accessed the FAQs create page','admin/cms/faqs/create','{}','{}','','2026-05-13 13:55:05','2026-05-13 13:55:05','faqs'),(2140,'1','105.160.6.33','Unknown','4','store',NULL,'User created a new FAQ: Are ECDE services free in Laikipia County?','admin/cms/faqs','{}','{\"question\":\"Are ECDE services free in Laikipia County?\",\"answer\":\"Most ECDE services are subsidized by the County Government, but some centres may charge minimal fees for meals or facilities.\",\"status\":\"published\",\"order\":4,\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-13T13:55:18.000000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2026-05-13T13:55:18.000000Z\",\"id\":4}','','2026-05-13 13:55:18','2026-05-13 13:55:18','faqs'),(2141,'1','105.160.6.33','Unknown','0','index',NULL,'User accessed the FAQs index page','admin/cms/faqs','{}','{}','','2026-05-13 13:55:18','2026-05-13 13:55:18','faqs'),(2142,'1','105.160.6.33','Unknown','0','create',NULL,'User accessed the FAQs create page','admin/cms/faqs/create','{}','{}','','2026-05-13 13:55:22','2026-05-13 13:55:22','faqs'),(2143,'1','105.160.6.33','Unknown','5','store',NULL,'User created a new FAQ: Why was the ECDE-MIS introduced?','admin/cms/faqs','{}','{\"question\":\"Why was the ECDE-MIS introduced?\",\"answer\":\"It was introduced to improve data accuracy, enhance planning, and support efficient service delivery across all ECDE centres.\",\"status\":\"published\",\"order\":5,\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-13T13:55:44.000000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2026-05-13T13:55:44.000000Z\",\"id\":5}','','2026-05-13 13:55:44','2026-05-13 13:55:44','faqs'),(2144,'1','105.160.6.33','Unkn